# P4NR Development Pipeline — v5 OSS

Public LTS line: `node-red-contrib-modbus` v5.x.

## Repo Boundary

| v5 OSS (this repo) | v6 closed (`P4NR/modbus/...`) |
|--------------------|-------------------------------|
| Public GitHub PRs | Private next major |
| Server in-package | Server split out |
| No TLS | Modbus-Client-TLS |
| `debug` logging | `winston` |

## Teams

| Team | Agent | Writes |
|------|-------|--------|
| 1 | `p4nr-spec-author` | `docs/p4nr/capabilities/`, `plans/` |
| 2 | `p4nr-spec-reviewer` | `docs/p4nr/reviews/` |
| 3 | `p4nr-developer` | `src/`, `test/` (after APPROVE) |

Flow: Team 1 → Team 2 → GATE 1 → Team 3 → GATE 2.

## OSS Rules

1. No code before APPROVE in `docs/p4nr/reviews/`
2. Backwards compatibility in v5 — breaking changes need spec justification
3. User-visible changes need CHANGELOG entry
4. After `src/` changes: `npm run build`
5. Node tests: Mocha + test-helper only
